snippet.title: Blue Blood Trailer - Out Now!
snippet.description:
Once a year, the bloodiest gala of the year, The Scarlet Ball, is held within the deep, sprawling halls of The Smythe Estate. Grab a glass. You're here to murder its host.

Blue Blood, an RPG Maker slasher-horror game, is out now on itch.io!

itch.io: https://jaspers.itch.io/blue-blood
twitter: https://twitter.com/CatNamedJaspers
